        {
            "title": "美伊暫時解除荷姆茲海峽封鎖後美國國債收益率大幅下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/X04OPFc9T5ezNvoK5.L_0g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA5T0IM_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週五美國國債收益率大幅下跌,此前伊朗和美國宣布在以色列與黎巴嫩停火期間暫時重新開放<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"荷姆茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:荷姆茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/荷姆茲海峽\">荷姆茲海峽</a>,這增強了市場對這一關鍵瓶頸恢復供應流動的希望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗外交部長阿拉格奇(Abbas Araghchi)在X平台上發文表示:「配合黎巴嫩停火協議,荷姆茲海峽對所有商業船隻的通行在停火期間的剩餘時間內宣布完全開放。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統川普在社交媒體上注意到這一決定後寫道:「伊朗剛剛宣布伊朗海峽完全開放並準備好全面通行。謝謝!」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4af33097-d1a1-392e-8313-66d6396a9264-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普此前宣布以色列與黎巴嫩之間實施為期10天的停火,該停火協議在週五下午似乎仍在維持。以色列持續對黎巴嫩真主黨目標的攻擊一直是美國與伊朗談判中的癥結點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">稍早,川普還暗示華盛頓與德黑蘭之間的談判可能在本週末恢復。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普表示,美國和伊朗「非常接近」達成協議,並補充說伊朗已同意在20多年內不擁有核武器。川普曾表示,遏制伊朗的核野心是這場戰爭的核心原因,這場戰爭始於2月下旬美國和以色列對伊朗的聯合打擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為回報,伊朗呼籲取消國際制裁。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普表示,如果華盛頓接近與德黑蘭達成協議,他將考慮延長原定於本月底到期的與伊朗的臨時停火協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Axios報導稱,知情官員透露,雙方正在討論一份三頁的計劃以結束衝突。該提案的一部分內容包括美國釋放200億美元的凍結伊朗資金,以換取伊朗同意放棄其濃縮鈾。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷姆茲海峽解除封鎖的前景以及和平談判取得進展的跡象,支撐了市場對聯準會可能在今年稍後大幅降息的新一輪押注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">衝突引發的能源衝擊曾引發對通膨壓力飆升的擔憂,這可能迫使全球央行考慮提高借貸成本。在荷姆茲海峽重新開放的消息宣布後,油價暴跌,跌破每桶90美元,但仍高於戰前水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間上午10:22(格林威治標準時間14:22),基準10年期美國國債收益率下跌80個點子至4.232%,而對聯準會利率預期特別敏感的2年期國債收益率下跌72個點子至3.706%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%A4%E8%8D%B7%E5%A7%86%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E5%BE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E6%94%B6%E7%9B%8A%E7%8E%87%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-153301359.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 23:49:32",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普稱伊朗正清除霍爾木茲海峽的水雷",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 川普表示，伊朗正在清除<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"霍爾木茲海峽\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:霍爾木茲海峽;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/霍爾木茲海峽\">霍爾木茲海峽</a>的水雷，此舉可能會擴大這條重要水道的商業航運。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普周五在社媒發帖稱，德黑蘭「在美國的幫助下已經或正在清除」霍爾木茲海峽的所有水雷。川普的說法目前尚無法立即得到證實。《紐約時報》上周引述匿名美國官員報導稱，伊朗無法找到其埋設的所有地雷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗周五早些時候表示，將在以色列和黎巴嫩之間為期10天的停火期間開放霍爾木茲海峽，這增加了達成協議結束中東更廣泛戰爭的可能性。重新開放霍爾木茲海峽是川普4月7日宣布與伊朗停火的主要條件之一。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-18a092cf-4b37-3c94-8ccb-e2bd3f92160f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以色列與伊朗支持的真主黨之間的衝突，使結束這場曠日持久的中東戰爭變得更加複雜。儘管如此，川普周五堅稱「這項協議與黎巴嫩沒有任何關係」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Says Iran Is Removing Sea Mines From Strait of Hormuz</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%AD%A3%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4%E9%9C%8D%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%A8%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%B0%B4%E9%9B%B7-144249800.html",
